Title: Harry Munter
Actors: Jan Nielsen, Carl-Gustaf Lindstedt, Gun Jönsson, Georg Adelly
Plot: Harry Munter, a sensitive, kind, appealing man in his twenties, lives with his parents. He's an inventor, a bit of a mystic, maybe a genius, and a good son and grandson. He's offered work in the U.S. But a friend has cancer and the world is changing in ways that provoke profound sadness.
